*[http://www.media.utah.edu/UHE/c/CHURCHJESUSLATTER.html Utah History Encyclopedia]
*[http://www.ldstoday.com/ LDS Today] - News related to The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints
*[http://search.ldslibrary.com/ LDS Library] - Full text search engine; more than 3,300 important LDS books.
*[http://www.GrupoSUD.com GrupoSUD.com] - A large general interest Spanish-language discussion list for LDS Church members.
*[http://www.mormonwiki.com Mormon wiki] - Wiki for and supported by Latter-day Saints
*[http://ldsfaq.byu.edu/ LDSFAQ at byu.edu] - A comprehensive index answering many common questions. Uses large portions of The Encyclopedia of Mormonism
*[http://www.mormonmomma.com Mormon Momma] - scholarship and fellowship for LDS women
*[http://www.ldsaudio.com/free-book-of-mormon/ Audio Book of Mormon] - free download, mp3 format
*[http://www.theldswoman.com The LDS Woman] - Free online social network and magazine for LDS women.
*[http://mormonismsearch.net Mormonism Search] - Search Mormon Web Sites - Browser Plugin Available

